{"tid":2354813,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陸永拍無綫劇停機即戴罩 工作人員懶理風險「戴半罩」","createTime":"2021-01-05T18:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T08:31:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06582c1449325ca7442d7fd89b72d362c3156d24","tid":2354813,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"日前有一對情侶搭昂坪巴士拒戴好口罩惹眾怒，原來有些人習慣「戴半罩」，近日陸永有份演的無綫劇《智能愛(AI)人》，講他要周旋在李佳芯及馮盈盈之間，不知令幾多宅男羨慕，之不過在場多名工作人員都是「戴半罩」，防疫意識欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n日前陸永單拖為《智能愛(AI)人》劇在石硤尾一行人天橋進行拍攝，同場還有20多名臨時演員，連同工作人員有近40多人在現場。等埋位時陸永留在化妝車，既可以休息又可以減少同大群人接觸。至於在場其他人，防疫意識較差，不少都半褪下口罩，更有工作人員將口罩拉至下巴，變相等如沒有戴，不過當他們發現有記者在場時，各人紛紛戴回口罩。<br />\n<br />\n陸永當時離開化妝小巴，臨開工前他跟助手急急腳，走到附近便利店買朱古力食，然後他行到上天橋跟一班臨時演員試位，現場所見只有陸永穿淺色服裝，其餘臨時演員清一色着黑色衫，部份演員更套上綠色手袖、頭套，相信是作後期CG加工之用。他們在天橋上以機械式步伐慢行，前後試3、4趟後，到正式拍攝，各人才脫下口罩。當拍攝完畢，陸永非常錫身，急忙戴回口罩，慎防感染，當日大概拍到6時許，拍了一個鏡頭就收工。<br />\n<br />\n此外，早前有一名TVB外判道具員工確診，理論上應該加倍小心，不過見拍攝當日工作人員仍企得密集，似乎有點牙煙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BvAefVFnkdlamhEq5xcqQQr1YPw=/802x517/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DCN3QDL4HJEJZLK6UX4UNC7SA4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBvAefVFnkdlamhEq5xcqQQr1YPw%3D%2F802x517%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDCN3QDL4HJEJZLK6UX4UNC7SA4.JPG&h=07b6038b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ih8I-xqwGwCqQ7ON0zd4LxCnfZA=/802x1221/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/53HUDQQGH5HUXFKLLVKOL5PYVI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fih8I-xqwGwCqQ7ON0zd4LxCnfZA%3D%2F802x1221%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F53HUDQQGH5HUXFKLLVKOL5PYVI.JPG&h=dc077cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7m9QEfkbBYyDZNucPMJJXX-dcdo=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B6KNRZBIHNDLRLI4NRUVIPGFBQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7m9QEfkbBYyDZNucPMJJXX-dcdo%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB6KNRZBIHNDLRLI4NRUVIPGFBQ.JPG&h=f875330a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210106/6UZNV2RTXBG3JEDFBQRUWO2TPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2F6UZNV2RTXBG3JEDFBQRUWO2TPQ%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=ed8e0144\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210106%2F6UZNV2RTXBG3JEDFBQRUWO2TPQ%2F&h=a265c924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210106/6UZNV2RTXBG3JEDFBQRUWO2TPQ/</a>"},{"pid":"74cf5eadb29a67b2f8d3933cc5d5acbba38cab84","tid":2354813,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":88,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"個助手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e9a640ac1e0b69c02b81cdd35742826de25b83","tid":2354813,"uid":16659,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"quote":{"pid":"74cf5eadb29a67b2f8d3933cc5d5acbba38cab84","tid":2354813,"uid":301989,"like":4,"dislike":88,"score":-84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"個助手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"師兄食咁偏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba8c65ae60c293948a042abb35ad4c9e185872","tid":2354813,"uid":27664,"like":98,"dislike":5,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"真係好On9，除吓又再戴吓，自我感覺良好，Cctvb班友仲係覺得戴半罩、戴透明罩係對防疫有幫助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\